headline: TransDigm (TDG): 3 Reasons We Love This Stock
summary: Since June 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 88%. But one standout stock has more than doubled the market - over the past five years, TransDigm has surged 217% to $1,460 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 15.7% in the last six months, beating the S&P by 16.3%.
